sequenceDiagram
  actor U as caller (CLI / API)
  participant R as renderSvg / renderHtml
  participant P as prepare → layout()
  participant F as finishEdges
  participant G as geometry (FR6/FR7)
  participant S as svg.ts / native class·state svg
  participant RT as runtime twin (toSvgString)
  U->>R: render(dsl, { bridges })
  R->>P: layout(model, { theme, bridges })
  P->>F: finishEdges(edges, theme, bridges)
  F->>G: resolveLabelCollisions(plates)
  G-->>F: per-edge shifts → nudge labelPos (FR6)
  F->>G: applyEdgeBridges(edges, elbow && bridges ?? true)
  G-->>F: bridged d per hopping edge → edge.path (FR7)
  P-->>R: PositionedModel (labels de-collided, crossings bridged)
  R->>S: renderSvgFromModel(model) — bakes edge.path
  S-->>U: static SVG / PNG
  Note over RT: interactive HTML export re-runs the SAME FR6/FR7<br/>twins in buildSvg → dom-runtime-parity byte guard
